<h2>Reservation Confirmed!</h2>
<p>Hello {{ name }},</p>
<p>Your parking slot has been successfully booked.</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Slot Number:</strong> {{ slotNumber }}</li>
    <li><strong>Location:</strong> {{ location }}</li>
    <li><strong>Start Time:</strong> {{ startTime }}</li>
    <li><strong>End Time:</strong> {{ endTime }}</li>
</ul>
<p>Please arrive before {{ startTime }} or your reservation may expire.</p>
<p>Thank you for using Smart Parking!</p>
